Portuguese President Cavaco Silva to Meet Parties After Socrates Resigns

-- B y   A n a b e l a   R e i s
-- 
2011-03-23T21:23:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/portuguese-president-cavaco-silva-to-meet-parties-after-socrates-resigns.html
Portuguese President Anibal Cavaco
Silva will meet political parties represented in parliament on
March 25 after Prime Minister  Jose Socrates  presented his
resignation today.  The government will retain its full powers until the
president accepts the prime minister’s resignation, according to
a statement on the presidency’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anabela Reis in Lisbon at 
 areis1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joao Lima at 
 jlima1@bloomberg.net  